      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/vanguard-bluebay-bet-there-s-more-juice-in-boj-rate-hike-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管市场对今年进一步紧缩政策的预期已大幅下降，但仍有少数知名投资者押注日本未来几个月将进一步加息。]]></description>
